alcatelIND1DevicesMIB.description: This module describes an authoritative enterprise-specific Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) Management Information Base (MIB): This module provides Object Indentifier definitions for Chassis and Modules of the Alcatel Internetworking OmniSwitch 10000 Series Product Lines.
